<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The specific measure shall concern the Greek islands, with the exception of those which are not covered by a national regional aid scheme, viz. Salam&iacute;na, and, as far as aid for industrial investment is concerned, A&iacute;yina, &Iacute;dhra and Sp&eacute;tses. </inglise>
