<inglise> Article 7 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 7 </eesti>
<inglise> The special programme shall include the information provided for in the Annex to Regulation (EEC) No 2615/80. </inglise>
<eesti> Eriprogramm sisaldab m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2615/80 lisas s&auml;testatud teavet. Samuti sisaldab see: </eesti>
<inglise> It shall also include: (a) an analysis of requirements with regard to communications between the islands and mainland Greece and between the islands themselves, both as regards transport infrastructures and transport services, a description of existing aid schemes for such transport services, with details of average annual public expenditure thereunder; </inglise>
<eesti> a) anal&uuml;&uuml;si, mis k&auml;sitleb saarte ja Kreeka maismaa ja samuti saarte endi vaheliste &uuml;hendustega seotud vajadusi nii transpordi infrastruktuuri kui ka veoteenuste osas, kirjeldust olemasolevatest kavadest selliste veoteenuste toetamiseks ja andmeid nende kavade raames aastas keskmiselt tehtavate riiklike kulutuste kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) a description of requirements with regard to water quality analysis and waste treatment; </inglise>
<eesti> b) vee kvaliteedi anal&uuml;&uuml;si ja j&auml;&auml;tmek&auml;itlusega seotud vajaduste kirjeldust; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) in connection with the operations referred to in Article 4 (2): (i) a description of measures planned to aid transport services; </inglise>
