<inglise> (ii) the nature and location of the transport infrastructure; an installation programme covering waste treatment plant, water analysis equipment and sea-water desalination plant. </inglise>
<eesti> ii) transpordi infrastruktuuri laadi ja asukohta k&auml;sitlevaid andmeid; j&auml;&auml;tmek&auml;itlusrajatisi, veeanal&uuml;&uuml;siseadmeid ja merevee magestustehaseid k&auml;sitlevat teostuskava. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 8 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 8 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall not prejudice the current re-examination of the Fund Regulation provided for in Article 22 of that Regulation. </inglise>
